text: Icupima ampliata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins, Galileo and Tavakilian in 2008. It is known from French Guiana.BioLib.cz - Icupima ampliata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 2008
title: Icupima ampliata
